snippet.title: Vinemon: Sauce Edition - New Beginnings Trailer
snippet.description:
This is a video to showcase the updates we've made at the start of the game! Outside of the Disclaimers and Outro, the video is unedited! 

Thanks for watching and until next time... Peace!

---

Reminder - Vinemon: Sauce Edition is a Pokemon Parody. All rights related to Pokemon belong to Game Freak and Nintendo!

The game is dedicated to the Vinesauce community through RPG Maker XP with the Pokemon Essentials Plugin.

Sprites are made by our team and the community.

- Swone Vial Co Dev Team
